I'm 57 now and not so good at impressions anymore. I still sing Neil and Bruce in the shower, though.

Thanks so much, Neil! So glad you're still exercising your musical brain and invoking your built-in superpower, neuroplasticity.

"And when I hurt, the hurtin' runs off my shoulder. Who could be hurt when avoiding you!"

"None. Touching none. Reaching out, mentally, I won't touch you!"
